<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta name="ROBOTS" content="NOINDEX, NOFOLLOW">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to roomM8!</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="cosmo-bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="index.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="email.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="profile-card">
        <div class="inner-container">
            <div class="row profile-container message-title bg-primary" style="padding: 20px; text-align: left;">
                <h2>Welcome, <%= user.name.split(' ')[0] %>!</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="data-container">
                <div class="row">
                    <p>
                        Thank you for completing your profile on
                        <strong><a href="https://roomm8.io/">roomM8</a></strong>!
                    </p>
                    <br/>
                    <p>
                        Now that you have finished setting up your account, other
                        users on roomM8 will be able to see your profile and message you
                        if they are interested. You can also search through the entire
                        roomM8 database of Nooglers to find the perfect roommate for you.
                        If there aren't a lot of people showing up in your search results,
                        please be patient while more Nooglers continue to sign up.
                    </p>
                    <br/>
                    <p>
                        I sincerely hope you find roomM8 useful. If you experience any
                        problems, or wish to address any concerns, please feel free to 
                        reply to this email, or submit an issue on the 
                        <a href="https://github.com/SWalls/roomM8">roomM8 github repository</a>.
                    </p>
                    <h3 style="text-align: right;">Happy matching!</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="profile-card">
        <strong>Here is your completed profile:</strong>
    </div>
    <% var isUserRegistered = typeof user !== "undefined"; %>
    <% include ../partials/user-profile.ejs %>
    <div class="profile-card">
        <p>
            <strong>What's this?</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            You received this email because you signed up for roomM8, a web app designed
            to help Nooglers find roommates. To stop receiving messages in your inbox, head over to 
            <a href="https://roomm8.io/">roomM8.io</a>, where you can login
            and delete your profile.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you received this email by mistake, please ignore it. Thank you.
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>Privacy Policy</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            None of the information you provide to roomM8 will ever be given
            or sold to any third party, or used for any purpose other than
            providing you with the services explicitly outlined on the roomM8
            website. Period.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>